| Relationship | What do you want?                      | Django Field    | Where to put it         |
| ------------ | -------------------------------------- | --------------- | ----------------------- |
| One-to-One   | Each A has one B, each B has one A     | OneToOneField   | In “A or B” side model  |
| One-to-Many  | Many A have one B, each B has many A   | ForeignKey      | In “many” side model    |
| Many-to-Many | Many A have many B, many B have many A | ManyToManyField | In one model only       |
